title.narrative: EAPR has strengthened evidence, partnerships and resource mobilization capacity to improve NUTRITION outcomes.

description.narrative: Nutrition played lead role in EMM headline coordination; engagement across 6 sectors, including for PFM, PSE, C4D, urban, social protection, ECD and WASH. ASEAN nutrition consultant recruited and major UNICEF-proposed activities endorsed in 2018-2030 strategic plan, including a scorecard and standards and guidelines in key areas. UNICEF convenes active Asia UN network for SUN, which produced joint UN SOFI report and pursuing joint actions. Strengthened partnerships with 12 organizations, who contributed to a regional action framework for complementary feeding. MCN supplement “Triple Trouble” completed, total 19 scientific articles & lessons learned in regional capacity building for NiE. | Status:On-track | As-of Date:27/08/2020
